explanation: The objects involved in completing the task of placing the warmed plum, cooked egg, and heated potato in the green garbage can are the Potato (to place the heated potato), Fork or Spoon (to handle the warmed plum), Egg (to be thrown in the garbage can), Plate (to hold the warmed plum or cooked egg), and Knife (to cut or handle the warmed plum or cooked egg).
